newCmd('.write','','*v+11.4 adds the FILE option, function display, and image quality;clip','(application only; not applet). Writes information to a file or to the system clipboard. (For the clipboard, simply specify CLIPBOARD instead of a file name.) Options include: an image of the application screen, the script history, the current model state in the form of a script, the current molecular orbital in the form of a JVXL file, or the current isosurface in the form of a JVXL file. ','0|1','','')
